What is databricks cluster ??
Databricks cluster is nothing but a set of computational resource and some configuration on which
you can run your data engineering, data science and data analytics kind of workload such as you can
go for some kind of pipeline.

Got oto compute section in the databricks
All-Purpose Cluster vs Job Clusters

Aspect	                All-Purpose Clusters	                            Job Clusters
Purpose	                Interactive, collaborative analysis.	            Optimized for running specific jobs or workflows.
Use Case	Used for development, ad-hoc queries, or testing.	              Used for scheduled tasks like ETL, machine learning pipelines, or batch processing.
Lifecycle	Always running (can be manually started/stopped).             automatically created for the job and terminated after the job completes.



cluter configuration -- one driver node and 0 or more worker nodes